        Parameters:
        init_pop_mult - the multiple for the initial population
        num_workers - the number of worker threads for this manager
        max_num_reps - the maximum number of reproductions
        num_dofs - the number of dimensions for the individual
        size_x - the number of cells in x
        size_y - the number of cells in y
        ch_sp_x - the child spread in x, relative to the parent
        ch_sp_y - the child spread in y, relative to the parent
        mgr_id - the id of the population manager
        sel_type - the individual selection type,
        is_allow_dying - if true then individuals are dying after they had some number of children
        min_chld_cnt - the minimum number of children before dying
        max_chld_cnt - the maximum number of children before dying
